videos.description: Jeff Teague spins off his defender and sets Robert Williams up on the baseline for an and-1 finish for the Celtics.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Teague sets up Williams for and-1 bucket) 2021/02/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Teague sets up Williams for and-1 bucket

videos.description: Jayson Tatum takes it all the way to the rack and absorbs the contact from Kawhi Leonard as he flushes a one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Tatum flushes and-1 dunk

videos.description: Ivica Zubac receives the pass from Lou Williams and elevates to punch a dunk home over Tristan Thompson.
videos.headline: Zubac posterizes Thompson

videos.description: Kemba Walker comes up clutch as he nails a nice jumper to give the Celtics a 113-112 lead over the Clippers in the 4th.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kemba nails go-ahead bucket in Celtics win vs. Clippers) 2021/02/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kemba nails go-ahead bucket in Celtics win vs. Clippers
